import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"contacts"}}>{`Contacts`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"mailto:dave@yodata.io"}}>{`Dave Duran`}</MDXTag>{`, technical questions, schema, project contributions`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"mailto:curt@yodata.io"}}>{`Curt Schooling`}</MDXTag>{`, implementation support, consulting services`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"libraries--tools"}}>{`Libraries & Tools`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://www.npmjs.com/package/yodata-context"}}>{`Yodata Context`}</MDXTag>{`: simple, robust JSON data transformations without (much) code. `}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@yodata/event-router"}}>{`Yodata Event Router`}</MDXTag>{`: create and deploy event handling micro-services`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/Yodata/yodata-actions"}}>{`Yodata Actions`}</MDXTag>{`: produce consistent, compliant structured data in your applications`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://www.npmjs.com/package/yodata-inbox-poller"}}>{`Yodata Inbox Poller`}</MDXTag>{`: inbox polling service scaffold, easy deploy with docker`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"specifications"}}>{`Specifications`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://schema.org"}}>{`Schema.org`}</MDXTag>{` - mother of all all rdf schema vocabularies`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://www.w3.org/standards/techs/rdf#w3c_all"}}>{`Resource Description Framework (RDF)`}</MDXTag>{` - universal data serialization standard`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://www.w3.org/TR/ldn/"}}>{`Linked Data Notifications`}</MDXTag>{` - decentralized pub/sub`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/solid"}}>{`SOLID - Social Linked Data Application Framework`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"tutorials"}}>{`Tutorials`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://youtu.be/4x_xzT5eF5Q"}}>{`What is Linked Data [video]`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
